lyrics:
[verse]
Максим маленький гном, a gnome so small and kind
In the forest he would roam, a gentle heart you'll find
With a hat of red and pointy shoes, his magic always shines
Максим маленький гном, spreading joy with his rhymes

[chorus]
Oh Максим, little gnome, with a heart so true
Your laughter brings us home, your spirit shining through
Through mossy hills and secret trails, your presence makes us smile
Максим маленький гном, let your magic stay awhile
